<br>
Anyway, I'm finally at the point where my non-plane gear is about the best I can get. Actually, I've never even been to planes-sigh, and I prefer grouping to soloing any day. Druids have a rep as &quot;lootwhores,&quot; so I never get greedy and always try to share or give class specific items. But, it is hard to group occasionally. At this rate I will never ever get to the planes.<br>
<br>
Anyway, I need a shoulder slot item, and figure I may have to rely on myself. Currently using braided ivy cords. My AC self-buffed is 794, wis is 203. <br>
<br>
Was thinking meditative blanket or Oblus DEATH shroud (not the no drop one). That will get my AC over 800 self-buffed, and keep wisdom at 200.<br>
<br>
Currently load-out<br>
<br>
Face- Plat Ruby Veil<br>
Neck- C. Talisman<br>
Ears- Forrest loops (x2)<br>
Finger-+6 wis ring<br>
Finger- golem tear<br>
Hands- Paw gloves<br>
Arms- ES Vambraces or Hollow boned<br>
Chest- Shroud of Nature<br>
Belt- Muc. Girdle<br>
Head-Frog Crown<br>
Legs- gatorscale<br>
Back- Mammoth Cloak<br>
Hand-Paw of Opalla<br>
Shield-Sarnak Battleshield<br>
Wrists- RMB (x2)<br>
Feet- Eboots<br>
Shoulders- Braided Ivy Cords<br>
<br>
So, to make a long story short- How rare is Oblus Death Shroud in Seb? And is it one of those &quot;melee class first screw-the-druids-itmes&quot; that is impossible to lotto for? I play on solusek Ro and from what I've observed, Seb is always packed and camped to high heaven.<br>
<br>
And what is general cost on the item? I am broke right now as I just bought the sarnak shield. I got ripped off, but, I really wanted it (12.6k plat, Iksar Breastplate, runed circ, tattered mantle, 3 51+spells and some other bank junk).<br>
<br>
Any thoughts on the death shroud? Or thoughts on a different non-planes item load-out?<br>
